{"tid":2280914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西志願者參與新冠疫苗試驗後自殺亡","createTime":"2020-11-11T00:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:10:31.000Z","uid":358871,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"60b4f43570ed5e512bd5c98acdc702670bff7806","tid":2280914,"uid":358871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"巴西有傳媒報道，當地衛生監管機構暫停與中國科興生物的新型冠狀病毒疫苗臨床試驗，是由一宗自殺事件引起。<br />\n<br />\n巴西一間電視台在報道中表示，已經看過涉事實驗志願者的驗屍報告，指當事人是自殺。<br />\n<br />\n巴西衛生監管機構在當地星期一宣布，暫停有關試驗，表示在上月底的試驗中，出現嚴重不良反應，但無透露更多細節。巴西政府早前宣布，同意購買4600萬劑科興生物疫苗，並納入國家免疫計劃，明年初提供接種，但總統博爾索納羅其後表示，不會容許疫苗進口巴西，形容巴西人不會做「白老鼠」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMNdC2H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMNdC2H.png&h=6a6e8df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559331-20201111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559331-20201111.htm&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7ImHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4250d0b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559331-20201111.htm&h=52b9fccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559331-20201111.htm</a>"},{"pid":"44cc62b2050ffae541c15206375cedd71daa6a12","tid":2280914,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:40:36.000Z","msg":"被自殺"},{"pid":"3532a3f43929930e830cd8dfa4d3ad2eb0bcaee7","tid":2280914,"uid":76261,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"被自殺"},{"pid":"a94acb25024b5720a49e8410889edc22edaed88a","tid":2280914,"uid":90735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會變咗喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2765b3c31f335d153fc6f85cb3bda87e75527d94","tid":2280914,"uid":184581,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTim